yourname+    344    254  0 23:35 pts/1    00:00:00 grep --color=auto python

âœ… The process ID (PID) of bad.py is 342 (example).

ğŸ”¹ 3ï¸âƒ£ TERMINATE THE PROCESS

# Kill process using SIGKILL (replace PROCESS_ID with actual PID)
