âœ… This forcefully stops bad.py from consuming CPU resources.

ğŸ”¹ 4ï¸âƒ£ VERIFY PROCESS TERMINATION

ps -ef | grep python
âœ… If bad.py is no longer in the list, it has been successfully terminated.

